pageBody: This project started as a collaboration between a small group of private sector doctors and software engineers who felt the urgent need to act in the face of COVID-19. Within hours we were joined by over 30 individual volunteers, including researchers, data scientists, engineers, designers, copywriters and more - without whom this project would have been impossible. If you'd like to join our fight, and help #flattenthecurve, fill out the form above. If you're a developer and would like to launch this in your country or community, head on over to our [open source project on GitHub.](https://github.com/Insight-fit-open-source "Insight Fit Open Source")
